Zhengguo Gong and 8th Prince belong to the true blue division.

568
00:42:29,420 --> 00:42:31,780
He should be his supporter.

569
00:42:31,780 --> 00:42:35,700
Tou He'qi works for the Crown Prince.

570
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:38,720
They are targeting the Crown Prince.

571
00:42:40,260 --> 00:42:42,000
Unless,

572
