573
00:42:45,460 --> 00:42:47,820
Find out what His Majesty said.

574
00:42:47,820 --> 00:42:50,340
His Majesty was really serious, he ordered an investigation

575
00:42:53,060 --> 00:42:55,100
Jie'jie, why are you smiling?

576
00:42:58,020 --> 00:43:00,220
The knife that was hanging over my head

577
00:43:00,220 --> 00:43:02,660
has finally been removed.

578
00:43:02,660 --> 00:43:05,480
Jie'jie, what do you mean?

579
00:43:05,480 --> 00:43:08,160
Since His Majesty ordered an investigation of the Crown Prince's allies,

580
00:43:08,160 --> 00:43:11,760
