581
00:43:11,760 --> 00:43:16,060
Therefore, there is no reason for him to give me to the Crown Prince.

582
00:43:16,060 --> 00:43:18,300
Jie'jie, I still don't understand.

583
00:43:19,180 --> 00:43:21,220
If what they said is true,

584
00:43:21,220 --> 00:43:25,240
I am linked with two of Mongolia's great tribes.

585
00:43:25,240 --> 00:43:27,160
Why waste such a good advantage

586
00:43:27,160 --> 00:43:28,900
