587
00:43:30,640 --> 00:43:32,440
Jie'jie's reasons are good.

588
00:43:32,440 --> 00:43:34,660
Jie'jie, this is fate.

589
00:43:35,660 --> 00:43:37,100
I'll bring Jie'jie some good food.

590
00:43:37,100 --> 00:43:38,260
Thank you.

591
00:43:40,940 --> 00:43:42,780
I thought I would have to wait until next year.

592
00:43:42,780 --> 00:43:45,260
I never thought that now

593
00:43:45,260 --> 00:43:47,460
