594
00:43:48,820 --> 00:43:52,340
Looks like this time 4th Prince and 8th Prince worked together to attack the Crown Prince.

595
00:43:52,340 --> 00:43:54,480
I am only a catalyst.

596
00:44:40,980 --> 00:44:42,720
Imperial Father.

597
00:44:42,720 --> 00:44:44,680
This time Crown Prince's colluding with military officials

598
00:44:44,680 --> 00:44:46,360
