Why does 4th prince like magnolias?

605
00:46:11,320 --> 00:46:13,200
Come back.

606
00:46:17,580 --> 00:46:19,400
Greetings, Fourth Prince.

607
00:46:19,400 --> 00:46:20,860
Rise.

608
00:46:25,700 --> 00:46:27,280
This hairpin looks good on you.

609
00:46:27,280 --> 00:46:28,480
