610
00:46:29,580 --> 00:46:32,300
No reason, I thought 4th Prince would laugh at me.

611
00:46:32,300 --> 00:46:34,180
Reason?

612
00:46:34,180 --> 00:46:35,960
This magnolia hairpin,

613
00:46:35,960 --> 00:46:38,680
I have kept until now.

614
00:46:38,680 --> 00:46:40,540
I unknowingly put it on today.

615
00:46:42,460 --> 00:46:44,480
Afterward...

616
00:46:44,480 --> 00:46:46,100
